the bishop on e6, but it is doing its job of attacking the d5 knight. The only
piece that is underperforming is the knight on e7. This knight can be
relocated from e7 to c5 but how? Yes - Ng6-f8-d7-c5! Konstantin does know
where his pieces belong!} Ng6 15. g3 {Preventing Nf4 just in case.} Re8 $5 {
